 * This file defines the canonical architecture of
 * StageOS.
 *
 * Before creating a new file or moving logic,
 * consult this manifest first.
 *
 * GENERAL RULES
 * -----------------------------------------------
 * • Each OS owns one responsibility.
 * • Each feature has one canonical owner.
